function fizzBuzz(length, markers){
    	var output;
    	for(var i=1;i<=length;i++){
    		output = '';
    		var number;
    		var term;
    		for(var j=0;j<markers.length;j++){
    			number = markers[j].number;
    			term = markers[j].term;
    			if(i%number === 0){
    				output+=term;
    			}
    		}
    		if(output === '') {
    			output+=i;
    		}
    		print(output);
    	}
    }
